<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 12:24:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国官员称，布林肯向王毅表达了对台湾“挑衅行为”的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国国务院一名高级官员表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周六与中国外长王毅就台湾问题进行了广泛交谈，并对北京最近的“挑衅行为”表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:37:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>奥运会——四十年后，前中国乒乓球队友倪、曾在巴黎继续比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-four-decades-former-chinese-teammates-still-competing-2024-07-27/</link><description>倪夏莲和曾志颖曾是中国乒乓球队的队友，但从未在自己的出生地参加过奥运会。四十年后，他们都代表其他国家参加巴黎奥运会。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 10:52:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-four-decades-former-chinese-teammates-still-competing-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>跳水——中国女子横扫首金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinese-women-win-first-gold-they-begin-bid-clean-sweep-2024-07-27/</link><description>周六，陈艺文和常雅妮在双人跳板3米板比赛中夺冠，开启了中国队争夺全部八枚女子奥运跳水金牌的征程。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 10:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinese-women-win-first-gold-they-begin-bid-clean-sweep-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>射击——中国选手黄盛胜夺得巴黎奥运会首金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-huang-sheng-win-first-gold-paris-games-2024-07-27/</link><description>周六，在10米气步枪混合团体赛中，中国选手黄玉婷/盛立豪夺得巴黎奥运会首枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:31:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-huang-sheng-win-first-gold-paris-games-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”迫使中国东北地区疏散、工厂停工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</link><description>据官方新华社周六报道，由于台风“盖美”带来大雨，中国东北地区有超过 27,000 人被疏散，数百家工厂被勒令停产。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾完成与北京达成协议以来首次南海补给任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</link><description>菲律宾外交部表示，周六，菲律宾在有争议的南海浅滩顺利完成了向其部队进行的补给行动，这是与中国达成的旨在缓和紧张局势的新安排下的首次此类任务。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 05:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在谴责北京海上“升级行动”后会见了中国王毅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-wong-presses-myanmar-generals-change-tack-ahead-laos-summits-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周六在老挝举行的地区峰会上会见了中国外长王毅，数小时前，他批评了北京在南海“不断升级的非法行动”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-wong-presses-myanmar-generals-change-tack-ahead-laos-summits-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部要求法院驳回 TikTok 对打击法律的挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/usdoj-tells-court-reject-tiktok-challenge-crackdown-law-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国司法部周五晚间要求联邦上诉法院维持 4 月份的一项法律，要求中国字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前出售 TikTok 在美国的资产，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/usdoj-tells-court-reject-tiktok-challenge-crackdown-law-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长就美国部署导弹向菲律宾发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-foreign-minister-warns-philippines-over-us-missile-deployment-2024-07-27/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅就美国部署中程导弹向菲律宾发出警告，称此举可能加剧地区紧张局势并引发军备竞赛。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-foreign-minister-warns-philippines-over-us-missile-deployment-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管经济步履蹒跚，但6月份中国工业利润仍实现较快增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-post-faster-gains-june-despite-faltering-economy-2024-07-27/</link><description>周六官方数据显示，尽管企业正努力应对经济复苏不稳定、消费者信心下降的问题，但中国 6 月份工业利润增长较快。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 02:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-post-faster-gains-june-despite-faltering-economy-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦：新兴市场对中国工厂产能过剩表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周五表示，包括一些G20国家在内的新兴市场与她一样对中国工业产能过剩感到担忧，并应敦促北京改变其经济模式。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>上海推出138亿美元基金支持集成电路、生物医药、人工智能等领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国商业中心上海周五宣布提供 1000 亿元人民币（137.9 亿美元）的资金，以促进其集成电路、生物医药和人工智能 (AI) 产业的发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 与中国外长王毅会面后，其办公室周五表示，英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军队。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长表示中韩应避免外部干涉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-skorea-should-avoid-external-interference-chinese-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五对韩国外长表示，中韩应避免外部因素干扰，扩大共同利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-skorea-should-avoid-external-interference-chinese-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国进口伊朗原油在东北找到新市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-iranian-crude-imports-find-new-market-northeast-2024-07-26/</link><description>油轮追踪公司和贸易消息人士称，自去年年底以来，进口的伊朗原油一直流入港口和炼油城市大连，帮助该国的石油购买量维持在接近历史最高水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 07:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-iranian-crude-imports-find-new-market-northeast-2024-07-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>